      {
        "id": "comment-1",
        "type": "nodetool.workflows.base_node.Comment",
        "data": {
          "comment": "# 🎬 AI Product Launch Video Generator\n\nTurn a campaign brief and product image into a cinematic launch clip. A prompt node combines your inputs, an agent writes an image-to-video prompt, then an Image-to-Video model animates the product shot.\n\n**Pipeline:** Brief + Audience + Features + Image → Prompt → Agent → Image-to-Video\n\n**Try this:** choose a language model and video model, then swap the product image or rewrite the agent's system prompt for a different tone."
        },
        "ui_properties": {
          "position": {
            "x": -460,
            "y": -247
          },
          "zIndex": 0,
          "width": 437,
          "height": 340,
          "selectable": true,
          "bypassed": false
        },
        "dynamic_properties": {},
        "dynamic_outputs": {}
      },
      {
        "id": "4",
        "type": "nodetool.text.Prompt",
        "data": {
          "prompt": "Using the text and image inputs, write a video prompt for a single 16:9 product shot. Give clear instructions on the animations and movements in the video.\n\nRules:\n- Present tense, visually concrete; one clear camera move and one primary subject action.\n- Include: subject, setting, time-of-day, camera language (framing, angle, lens, movement), composition cues, lighting, 3–5 color anchors, atmosphere/texture, and realistic motion cues.\n- Emphasize the product and key features naturally within the scene for the target audience and tone.\n- Finish with constraints: no on-screen text, no logos, no watermarks, no glitches, no distorted anatomy.\n\nInputs:\n- Campaign brief: {{ brief }}\n- Target audience: {{ audience }}\n- Key features: {{ features }}"
        },
        "ui_properties": {
          "selected": false,
          "position": {
